1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:12,220
[My Unicorn Girl]

3
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:18,640
[Episode 22. The genius artist
and his secret assistant]

4
00:01:19,350 --> 00:01:20,560
Everything is packed.

5
00:01:23,010 --> 00:01:23,990
Put some strength into it.

6
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:25,300
Isn't that the class monitor?

7
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,120
Why isn't the vice monitor with him?

8
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,240
Come on.

9
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,400
What did you buy?

10
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:32,170
This is not for you.

11
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:34,170
Where is Sang Tian?

12
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:36,140
-Sang Tian?
-I don't know.

13
00:01:37,030 --> 00:01:38,910
[Something is off with Sang Tian today.]

14
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,840
[I bet it's your doing.]

15
00:01:41,610 --> 00:01:42,920
[The man should compromise.]

16
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,440
[You shouldn't upset her.]

17
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:47,920
[Are you trying to cheer her up
with just oden?]

18
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,440
[You need more than that.]

19
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,410
Sang Tian and Miao Miao!

20
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,960
I bought some drinks.

21
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,270
Come on, hand these out.

22
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,520
Thank you, Senior.

23
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,900
Stop calling me that.

24
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:06,000
Just "Miao Miao" will do.

25
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,240
Because from now on...

26
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:09,340
I am Sang Tian's girlfriend.

27
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,860
A new girlfriend.

28
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:16,840
What about that Milk Tea Girl?

29
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,120
Nonsense.

30
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,680
-Why can't I ask?
-[This guy is too calm?]

31
00:02:21,930 --> 00:02:23,460
[Is he really her boyfriend?]

32
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,320
Comes and goes like the wind.

33
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,940
Am I right? Tian Tian?

34
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,120
Senior is right.

35
00:02:30,370 --> 00:02:31,970
Stop calling me that.

36
00:02:32,050 --> 00:02:33,970
We've been together for so long.
That title makes me feel old.

37
00:02:36,810 --> 00:02:37,930
The teasing is killing me.

38
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,520
We are off to the training.

39
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,079
I'll leave you be.

40
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,680
-Goodbye, Senior.
-Goodbye.

41
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,960
Let's go.

42
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,090
Don't be a third wheel.

43
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:48,570
Your hair is a mess.

44
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:02,990
Senior Miao Miao.

45
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:05,190
Do you know...

46
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,570
the meaning of "Ti amo"?

47
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:10,040
It means I love you in Italian.

48
00:03:10,810 --> 00:03:12,080
It seems like everyone knows.

49
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,970
Except for one.

50
00:03:14,450 --> 00:03:15,790
He is such a simpleton.

51
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,440
Miao Miao, maybe you should go home.

52
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,800
I am headed for the training.
I'll see you later.

53
00:03:24,010 --> 00:03:26,810
No. I am skipping class today
just to be with you.

54
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,240
I have it already.

55
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:40,130
What are you laughing at?

56
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,570
She wants you to open
the bottle cap for her.

57
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,480
Boyfriends do that. Don't you get it?

58
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:48,360
It's the 21st century.
Set aside your manly pride.

59
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,630
It's all right, Tian Tian.

60
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:52,600
That's right.

61
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,510
Fine, as long as you're happy.

62
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:58,450
We are happy.

63
00:04:01,940 --> 00:04:03,300
I need to head home.

64
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:05,350
Remember to inform Coach Ma for me.

65
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:17,930
[Why is he going home?]

66
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,519
[Could it be...]

67
00:04:20,029 --> 00:04:21,430
[that he noticed something?]

68
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,160
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

69
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,960
Miss me, honey.

70
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,950
Chen Chen.

71
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:32,800
Chen Chen, hear me out.

72
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,250
Chen Chen, hear me...

73
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,800
You can't eat instant noodles.

74
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,680
-Let's get some decent food.
-I'm in a hurry.

75
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:42,050
Fine, wait here.

76
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:50,090
Hey, Ying Ying.

77
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,080
Well, I am still...

78
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,120
having a meeting.

79
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:58,560
We will watch a midnight movie together.

80
00:04:58,850 --> 00:04:59,810
You miss me?

81
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:18,170
Chen Chen.

82
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:20,650
Instant noodle and ham.

83
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,890
It's like a mash of
Chen Chen and Qin Lang.

84
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,440
Enjoy.

85
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:31,040
The way you eat is so cute.

86
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:35,110
I'll call you my Little Piggy from now on.

87
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:39,310
Little Piggy.

88
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,940
I...

89
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:42,480
It's you again!

90
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,240
You pay for your actions sooner or later.

91
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:46,640
Listen closely.

92
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,159
Stop bothering me and Chen Chen.

93
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,840
Stop now or I am calling the police.

94
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,960
Scoundrel.

95
00:05:52,530 --> 00:05:54,680
-But...
-Do you mind explaining yourself?

96
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,550
What is this?

97
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,960
All of these are the girls you are dating.

98
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,600
What?

99
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,440
First, I am not a scoundrel.

100
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,760
My name is Qin Lang.

101
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,840
Secondly, I don't know them at all.

102
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,510
Chen Chen, let's go.

103
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,840
I want you to explain.

104
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,760
I...

105
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,080
It's not like he can.

106
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,420
Let me tell you the story.

107
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,880
Little Bunny, receptionist of bar.

108
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,910
Ying Ying, student of dancing academy.

109
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,760
Little Cutie, owner of TaoBao store.

110
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,160
And there is Little Piggy.

111
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:25,410
I gave Chen Chen that nickname...

112
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:29,400
Wait. Chen Chen, hear me out.

113
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,760
They are all my sisters.

114
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,409
They are here for groceries.

115
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,080
-He is framing me.
-Sisters, right?

116
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,200
Fine, I will make a phone call.

117
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,400
Let's see if I'm framing you.

118
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,500
Brother!

119
00:06:42,370 --> 00:06:43,890
So it's true.

120
00:06:54,130 --> 00:06:55,210
It's true.

121
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:56,560
So what?

122
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,530
Love is a matter of...

123
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,410
dating whoever you like.

124
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,990
Break up when it doesn't work.

125
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,360
I didn't point a gun at you
to make you do it.

126
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:06,740
One more thing.

127
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,240
A piece of advice.

128
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,560
With your bad temper...

129
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,180
and your hypocrisy,

130
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,560
I doubt you will ever get married.

131
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,890
Jerk!

132
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,480
Let's go.

133
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,230
Just now,

134
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,690
Thank you.

135
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,520
Don't mention it.

136
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,320
I don't like that guy anyway.

137
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,440
This is embarrassing.

138
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,520
Not at all.

139
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,080
Every young lady...

140
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,590
has a crush on a jerk.

141
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,920
Fair point.

142
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,220
And with you in the equation,

143
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,040
that makes two.

144
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:26,250
I don't like the way you put it.

145
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:29,680
You compare me with
that world class scoundrel?

146
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,640
This is a humiliation
to my honour and pride.

147
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:35,159
So you will be...

148
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,919
the normal harmless jerk.

149
00:08:37,090 --> 00:08:38,200
How does that sound?

150
00:08:38,690 --> 00:08:40,010
Why did that sound like...

151
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,169
it's worse than before?

152
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,330
Who says so?

153
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,480
A normal jerk is not hopeless.

154
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,640
"A normal jerk is not hopeless"?

155
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:59,070
Chen Chen, do you mean...

156
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,830
I can have another chance at you?

157
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,780
Wait for me!

158
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:11,800
Sang Tian.

159
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,620
Why are you so sweaty?

160
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:15,560
-You must be exhausted.
-Over there.

161
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:17,600
-Here, have some water.
-What is going on with them?

162
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:19,000
This is so sweet!

163
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,840
Senior is so thoughtful.

164
00:09:22,410 --> 00:09:23,330
Come.

165
00:09:24,130 --> 00:09:25,090
Let's go.

166
00:09:26,770 --> 00:09:27,690
Let's go.

167
00:09:28,210 --> 00:09:29,680
-Come.
-Feeling warm?

168
00:09:33,690 --> 00:09:34,770
Senior Miao Miao?

169
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,440
I've been thinking.

170
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:41,790
I can't be in a relationship with you.

171
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,220
Because...

172
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,250
You don't like girls?

173
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,240
No.

174
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,480
Because...

175
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,610
I...

176
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,470
have always been a girl.

177
00:09:56,250 --> 00:09:57,200
Silly!

178
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,600
You don't seem surprised.

179
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:01,380
I knew that a long time ago.

180
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:04,760
I also overheard your conversation
about getting a girlfriend.

181
00:10:07,010 --> 00:10:09,010
[That gestures you make
with your hands...]

182
00:10:09,090 --> 00:10:11,010
[are so elegant and captivating.]

183
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,720
[Even I can't do that.]

184
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,630
So you knew...

185
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,240
the moment you first saw me?

186
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,760
Of course. Otherwise I wouldn't help
with your homework.

187
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:28,870
Because you were supposed to be
my junior from Figure Skating Department.

188
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:33,380
I didn't do well in the test.

189
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,300
So I didn't make it.

190
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,750
Do you still regret it?

191
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:40,630
I was devastated at the time.

192
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,690
But then I joined Ice Hockey Department.

193
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,360
I realised...

194
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,310
I am not that into figure skating.

195
00:10:48,130 --> 00:10:51,120
So, you slowly fell in love
with ice hockey?

196
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,280
You can put it that way.

197
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:56,880
Did you fall in love with the sport
because of a particular someone?

198
00:10:57,120 --> 00:11:01,240
You could even tell that?

199
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,280
Of course, I know everything.

200
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,810
But I also know that...

201
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:06,480
something means a lot to you.

202
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,280
What is it?

203
00:11:09,810 --> 00:11:10,980
Judging by my observation...

204
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:12,860
and speculation on that boy,

205
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:15,400
I think it's safe to say that...

206
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,760
he knows you are a girl.

207
00:11:18,290 --> 00:11:19,260
What?

208
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:21,720
I bet you have questions for him.

209
00:11:21,930 --> 00:11:22,890
Go on.

210
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,320
Thank you, Senior Miao Miao.

211
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,320
Go on. Go.

212
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,800
I'll go now.

213
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,220
Again?

214
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:46,450
Hurry up.

215
00:11:48,970 --> 00:11:49,990
Senior Miao Miao.

216
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,320
Senior, you can't leave.

217
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,230
My captain wants to talk to you.

218
00:11:55,370 --> 00:11:56,850
What is it this time?

219
00:11:58,160 --> 00:12:01,160
Are you really dating Sang Tian?

220
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,540
None of your concern.

221
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:08,030
I don't understand.

222
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,480
What do you even like about him?

223
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,120
Shen Qiao Di from Qianbei University,

224
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,800
the guy who crushed you...

225
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,600
during the high school league last year,

226
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,760
Sang Tian was the first to challenge him.

227
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,720
He should have known better.

228
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:21,200
I disagree.

229
00:12:21,610 --> 00:12:22,730
In this world we live in,

230
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:24,690
plenty of people take action
based on confidence.

231
00:12:24,930 --> 00:12:26,570
Such as you, Meng Qi.

232
00:12:27,170 --> 00:12:28,730
People think you are outstanding.

233
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,880
But I like the way
Sang Tian challenged the impossible.

234
00:12:31,010 --> 00:12:32,850
I like how Sang Tian was so fearless.

235
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:37,860
Miao Miao, will you give me
another chance?

236
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:38,930
We'll talk...

237
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:42,180
when you can stop ordering your men...

238
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,280
to do your bidding.

239
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,000
Senior Miao Miao!

240
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:48,090
Captain, go after her.

241
00:12:49,930 --> 00:12:51,850
When I win
the University Ice Hockey League,

242
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,310
I will win her back.

243
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,760
Did you ask Sang Tian to get a girlfriend?

244
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,820
Does Sang Tian have one now?

245
00:13:03,530 --> 00:13:05,250
Shouldn't you feel happy for him?

246
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,260
You interfered in my choice of school,

247
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,640
and now you interfere in my social life.

248
00:13:10,050 --> 00:13:11,090
Right?

249
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,640
You want me out of your hair,

250
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,240
but do you even know...

251
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:17,550
what should and shouldn't be done
among friends?

252
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,250
I know well enough.

253
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:20,840
Really?

254
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:23,880
See for yourself.

255
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:32,680
That's why he's been acting odd.

256
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,560
How can you still smile about it?

257
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,360
Do you know what you are doing?

258
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:40,560
You are both men.

259
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:42,140
This is outrageous.

260
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,790
You're even living with him.

261
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:54,580
Mum, you don't understand.

262
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,090
What do you mean?

263
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,320
From the moment I got into
Liuye Sports University,

264
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,720
I already knew she was a girl.

265
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:05,160
If you knew she was a girl,

266
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,840
how could you allow her...

267
00:14:06,920 --> 00:14:08,800
to live in your dormitory?

268
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:10,010
You got it all wrong.

269
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,500
She was the one who refused,

270
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,200
not me.

271
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,840
So you wanted to live
in the same room with her?

272
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:22,680
Mum.

273
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:25,240
Sang Tian is not like what you think.

274
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,930
The reason why she disguised as a boy...

275
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,160
is because her mother studied
at Liuye Sports University.

276
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:34,840
That's the place where she finds
her connection with her mother.

277
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:37,960
Also, when we had a fight last time,

278
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:40,560
she was there to console me
and cheer me up.

279
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,760
She told me that
she was envious of my life.

