00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:54,080
going to get some food?

563
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,200
Come on.

564
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,420
Something is not right.

565
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:03,880
After so long,
you finally bought me some oden.

566
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,470
I never forgot.

567
00:32:06,560 --> 00:32:08,160
I just didn't get the right timing.

568
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:10,880
So what makes the right timing?

569
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:13,290
We sneaked off to eat.

570
00:32:13,370 --> 00:32:14,530
We need to keep it down.

571
00:32:22,260 --> 00:32:23,440
Hurry up and eat.

572
00:32:23,530 --> 00:32:24,850
You have to go home later.

573
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,650
I am taking my time with this.

574
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:28,040
I can't see you at home.

575
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:32,070
When were you so smooth?

576
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:43,560
Can't they pick
another day for renovation?

577
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:45,600
Now I can't have my hotpot.

578
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:46,960
We can get some oden.

579
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:48,150
It's been so long.

580
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:51,480
I can treat you to hotpot.

581
00:32:52,010 --> 00:32:53,450
-That should do it.
-Let's go.

582
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:55,470
Isn't that the vice monitor?

583
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:57,420
Sang Tian?

584
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,960
Vice Monitor, what are you doing here?

585
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,210
Isn't that...

586
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:09,420
Class Monitor? Why is he here?

587
00:33:10,030 --> 00:33:11,070
Class Monitor.

588
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:15,880
What are the odds?

589
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:18,920
Maybe we can join the tables
and eat together.

590
00:33:19,120 --> 00:33:20,160
How does that sound?

591
00:33:20,980 --> 00:33:22,000
Okay.

592
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:23,090
Great.

593
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,290
Have one.

594
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,350
-This fishball tastes good.
-Wen Bing.

595
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:42,130
Aren't you meeting Meng Na?

596
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:43,700
You have a date too, right?

597
00:33:43,780 --> 00:33:45,720
So why are you two here now?

598
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:49,250
She stood me up.

599
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:52,220
What are the odds, me too.

600
00:33:52,320 --> 00:33:53,510
Poor things.

601
00:33:53,950 --> 00:33:55,680
You two are the Stood-Up Brothers.

602
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:57,600
We asked you to join us for hotpot.

603
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:59,530
You should've joined us.

604
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,350
You two deserved it.

605
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,700
You should've joined us but you refused.

606
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:06,240
-You just have to come on your own.
-That's right.

607
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,400
Women are trouble.

608
00:34:09,239 --> 00:34:10,330
Right, Sang Tian?

609
00:34:10,719 --> 00:34:11,840
Yes.

610
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:13,730
Women are so troublesome.

611
00:34:35,489 --> 00:34:36,810
So that's what it is.

612
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:39,980
Have you decided
who you are in love with?

613
00:34:40,139 --> 00:34:41,960
I don't know.

614
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:45,199
I thought I would choose Wen Bing
to be my only love.

615
00:34:46,199 --> 00:34:47,320
But in the end...

616
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:50,199
But recently... I...

617
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,850
I keep thinking about Kidney Hurt.

618
00:34:55,159 --> 00:34:57,080
We'll have a game. Don't overthink.

619
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,680
Just let me know what you choice is.

620
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,600
-Left or right?
-Left.

621
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:02,160
-Coffee or tea?
-Tea.

622
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,720
-Winter or summer?
-Winter.

623
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:05,280
-Wen Bing or Kidney Hurt?
-Kidney Hurt.

624
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:13,890
He's been trying to ask you out, right?

625
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:15,160
Text him.

626
00:35:16,450 --> 00:35:18,500
Is that really necessary?

627
00:35:19,460 --> 00:35:20,340
Let me do it.

628
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,410
[Meet me at
Liuye Sports University at 9 p.m.]

629
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,200
Done.

630
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,120
You asked him out?

631
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:31,160
Go on.

632
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:57,920
Hello?

633
00:35:58,330 --> 00:35:59,930
What are you doing now?

634
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:03,490
I am just checking if you've
turned the room into a pig sty.

635
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:05,240
[You are the pig.]

636
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:08,080
Why aren't you saying "Ti amo"?

637
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:09,730
You won't fool me.

638
00:36:10,290 --> 00:36:12,100
-Sang Tian.
-[Hurry up.]

639
00:36:12,170 --> 00:36:13,770
[Come on, take the vantage point.]

640
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:18,000
She hung up on me.

641
00:36:18,190 --> 00:36:19,230
You...

642
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,350
Hurry up!

643
00:36:20,560 --> 00:36:22,160
Sang Tian, come here!

644
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,480
How is the network?

645
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:29,590
[Huang Hao Ran and Xiao Xiao
are here to watch the game.]

646
00:36:29,680 --> 00:36:30,810
[I'll talk to you later.]

647
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:34,920
[Why can't you remember to lock the door?]

648
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,480
[This is what happens.]

649
00:36:36,560 --> 00:36:37,960
[The whole room is filled with guys.]

650
00:36:39,490 --> 00:36:40,760
[They better not cause any trouble.]

651
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:44,040
[I am not getting a reply.]

652
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,720
-Give me the Cola.
-[Is he mad at me?]

653
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:46,960
Sang Tian, hurry up.

654
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:52,040
Sang Tian. What are you hiding?

655
00:36:52,580 --> 00:36:53,560
Show us.

656
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:55,400
Xiao Xiao, don't look at it.

657
00:36:57,040 --> 00:36:58,760
The resemblance is uncanny.

658
00:36:58,840 --> 00:37:00,000
This is marvellous.

659
00:37:00,090 --> 00:37:01,290
Everyone, look!

660
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,000
It's like a photo.

661
00:37:07,080 --> 00:37:08,920
Whose work is this? This is remarkable.

662
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,740
The person who drew this
must be in love with you.

663
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:13,920
And look, each of these
is a moment from his life.

664
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:16,720
This could only be someone close to you
in real life.

665
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,640
Could it be...

666
00:37:21,330 --> 00:37:22,360
I drew that.

667
00:37:23,340 --> 00:37:24,330
Forget it, Wei Lian.

668
00:37:24,410 --> 00:37:25,730
You can draw?

669
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,240
Why haven't we noticed before?

670
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,880
There is more you don't know.

671
00:37:28,970 --> 00:37:29,990
You can draw too?

672
00:37:31,660 --> 00:37:32,980
Then show us.

673
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:34,230
Show us.

674
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,410
-That should be nice.
-Show us.

675
00:37:36,530 --> 00:37:38,200
Come on. Draw a picture of me first.

676
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,830
Make me look macho.

677
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,140
Fine, but only one picture.

678
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:45,160
Come on, draw me. Hands at my waist,
or should I place them here?

679
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:46,840
A smiling face or a more serious look?

680
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,410
Should I show the dimple...

681
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:51,090
Make me slimmer. Stretch the legs, taller.

682
00:37:51,180 --> 00:37:52,420
It's a little short.

683
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,840
Should I undress?

684
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,840
Shen Wei Lian, is this a joke?

685
00:37:58,250 --> 00:37:59,170
Look!

686
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:02,880
Please, what is this?

687
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:05,320
Come up with better lies
the next time you bluff.

688
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,120
You don't understand.

689
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:08,280
This is abstract art.

690
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:09,440
This is a work of art.

691
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:10,560
Get it?

692
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:12,240
I don't know about abstract,

693
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:13,440
but I want to punch you.

694
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:15,280
-Don't fight.
-Sang Tian.

695
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:17,310
Be honest with us.

696
00:38:17,450 --> 00:38:18,490
Who drew this?

697
00:38:19,170 --> 00:38:20,640
Stop making us guess.

698
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,880
Tell us. Who was it?

699
00:38:23,810 --> 00:38:24,730
It was me.

700
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:28,880
Stop bluffing.

701
00:38:28,980 --> 00:38:30,760
Wei Lian just played us for fools.

702
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:32,280
So don't bother. It's pointless.

703
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,240
That's right.

704
00:38:34,310 --> 00:38:36,160
Who drew this?
This is very well done.

705
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:38,440
There is something...

706
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:39,900
I've been hiding from everyone.

707
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:41,560
I haven't told any of you.

708
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:43,530
But since you found out,

709
00:38:43,810 --> 00:38:45,010
then I shall confess.

710
00:38:45,610 --> 00:38:46,720
-What is it?
-What?

711
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:48,720
[This kid is insane.]

712
00:38:49,080 --> 00:38:50,280
[If you want to make it official,]

713
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:52,360
[at least discuss with
Sang Tian beforehand.]

714
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,180
The truth is,

715
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,320
I am a genuine artist.

716
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,050
That is lame.

717
00:39:01,290 --> 00:39:02,590
When I have free time,

718
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,970
I use him as the model...

719
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:06,360
for my drawing practice.

720
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:09,890
I see.

721
00:39:10,390 --> 00:39:11,640
Since the prodigy is here,

722
00:39:11,720 --> 00:39:13,080
why don't you draw us one...

723
00:39:13,160 --> 00:39:14,810
that is less abstract?

724
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,800
-Sure.
-He...

725
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:18,330
He can't.

726
00:39:18,530 --> 00:39:20,090
Give me ten minutes.

727
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:22,880
I need to discuss the sketch
with my assistant.

728
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:24,860
Who is your assistant?

729
00:39:26,720 --> 00:39:27,600
Him.

730
00:39:31,760 --> 00:39:33,080
What are you talking about?

731
00:39:33,160 --> 00:39:35,060
You have prosopagnosia.
How are you supposed to draw?

732
00:39:43,450 --> 00:39:45,290
I must say my handsomeness
is earth-shattering.

733
00:39:46,460 --> 00:39:48,030
That's why you fell for me.

734
00:39:53,490 --> 00:39:54,500
You have class.

735
00:39:58,890 --> 00:40:00,250
Am I...

736
00:40:01,090 --> 00:40:03,330
having some problem with my taste?

737
00:40:21,270 --> 00:40:22,150
It's done.

738
00:40:23,380 --> 00:40:25,460
This is pretty much a photo.

739
00:40:25,810 --> 00:40:27,770
The work of a genius indeed.

740
00:40:28,660 --> 00:40:30,420
Thanks to my assistant.

741
00:40:31,370 --> 00:40:32,740
I want to be your assistant.

742
00:40:33,250 --> 00:40:34,730
You can't make it, let me have the job.

743
00:40:34,810 --> 00:40:36,250
-Me too!
-Let me do it.

744
00:40:36,330 --> 00:40:37,330
-No.
-Stop, I get the job.

745
00:40:37,410 --> 00:40:38,740
You all should forget about it.

746
00:40:39,730 --> 00:40:41,910
So we are calling it a day.

747
00:40:41,990 --> 00:40:43,200
Come earlier next time.

748
00:40:43,420 --> 00:40:45,210
-Party-pooper.
-You are no fun.

749
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:47,210
All right, we're going back to our rooms.

750
00:40:47,290 --> 00:40:48,330
Goodbye.

751
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,930
-Bye.
-Goodbye.

752
00:40:56,790 --> 00:40:59,820
I don't think you came back...

753
00:40:59,970 --> 00:41:02,970
just to draw them a painting.

754
00:41:05,370 --> 00:41:07,360
I came back...

755
00:41:07,490 --> 00:41:08,680
because...

756
00:41:09,330 --> 00:41:10,460
Well...

757
00:41:18,410 --> 00:41:19,370
I am thirsty.

758
00:41:23,130 --> 00:41:26,730
Why do I feel like...

759
00:41:28,580 --> 00:41:29,570
you miss me too much?

760
00:41:36,010 --> 00:41:36,930
What?

761
00:41:37,610 --> 00:41:38,790
See your boss off.

762
00:41:42,090 --> 00:41:43,530
I know you miss me too much.

763
00:41:54,410 --> 00:41:56,130
I have one more dream.

764
00:41:56,460 --> 00:41:58,060
To hold a portrait exhibition.

765
00:41:58,330 --> 00:41:59,490
My little helper Sang Tian,

766
00:41:59,720 --> 00:42:01,000
will you help me out?

767
00:42:01,170 --> 00:42:02,290
I don't have the time.

768
00:42:02,410 --> 00:42:03,730
Ask Xiao Xiao.

769
00:42:03,810 --> 00:42:05,250
He would be happy to help.

770
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:07,920
Sang Zhan.

771
00:42:08,450 --> 00:42:09,630
-Sister.
-Why are you here?

772
00:42:12,210 --> 00:42:13,850
Actually I...

773
00:42:13,930 --> 00:42:15,320
-My brother is...
-Don't worry.

774
00:42:15,530 --> 00:42:16,810
I knew she's a girl.

775
00:42:18,890 --> 00:42:20,080
You knew?

776
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:23,530
You scared me. If you didn't know,
my sister could have...

777
00:42:24,050 --> 00:42:25,220
finished me off...

778
00:42:25,290 --> 00:42:26,680
Don't you dare bring that up.

779
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:29,800
She is your sister?
